com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.roads.match
Interface GeometryMatchEvaluator

All Known Implementing Classes:
OverlapMatchEvaluator, RoadSegmentMatchEvaluator
public interface GeometryMatchEvaluator

Computes a match confidence value for a given Geometry pair. Match values are in the range [0..1], with 1 indicating a better match than 0. A useful convention is that 0 indicates a match that is so poor it can be discarded (or not recorded for further processing).
